/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n~<br />\nPart B: 近幾年嘅DSE同埋AL Section E<br />\nCE可以做 但要做多D AL section E<br />\n因為依家DSE listening part B已經係用緊AL Section E嘅要求去定marking同task completion <br />\ndata file 唔可以照抄之餘 仲要轉字轉時地人 漏一個字都可以無分<br />\n你睇下AL Section E 嘅marking就知咩事"},{"pid":"eb58b2124d3cdfa953fa76ef31fd3bfcdad906f3","tid":2369783,"uid":367861,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T14:06:31.000Z","msg":"Part B<br />\n好撚易咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇task requirement 問要咩<br />\n自己喺data file抄入去"},{"pid":"8f5e26e10f8d6ae8374201014c8da610cbe2ddd4","tid":2369783,"uid":190187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"88dbf87d2c0a51bdce641c8a83027c273bd1d045","tid":2369783,"uid":305799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T13:07:31.000Z","msg":"當年學校係操教師評核試份listening<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T14:08:06.000Z","msg":"第一次聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629701b4d247a155d2fec16841835dc95956bac0","tid":2369783,"uid":190187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aec7d8035cc8fefcbb77763005c6673c10a1983e","tid":2369783,"uid":323845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T13:40:28.000Z","msg":"Part B 3個task用3支唔同色嘅螢光筆間point <br />\ndate要分好哂係邊個task 再mark低<br />\n做齊以上先好落筆寫 最忌邊做邊揾point 好嘥時間"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T14:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d40e934d049123982949ef3ec4d18ab84e3b4d0","tid":2369783,"uid":190187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0b553815150c4815f6898ae3f62cef975b118913","tid":2369783,"uid":48362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T13:58:19.000Z","msg":"學校